com.solacesystems.jms

Interface SolProducerEventSource


  • public interface SolProducerEventSource
    The SolProducerEventSource allows the application to set a SolProducerEventListener, used to receive SolProducerEvents. a MessageProducer created by the Solace JMS implementation can be cast to a SolProducerEventSource

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void setProducerEventListener(SolProducerEventListener listener)
      Called to set the SolProducerEventListener on a MessageProducer.

    • Method Detail

      • setProducerEventListener

        void setProducerEventListener(SolProducerEventListener listener)
        Called to set the SolProducerEventListener on a MessageProducer. It can be reset by using a null argument.
        Parameters:
        listener - The listener to set; null to clear the listener.

        Since:
        7.1.2
